Constructor Detail

DataRow.Headers

public DataRow.Headers(DataDriver source)
Constructs a new set of column headers. Gets the next row in source, and creates one column header per entry in the row. It is recommended to only use this on a freshly-created DataDriver.

Parameters:
source - The DataDriver to get columns from.
